    "This because the input numbers are uniformy distributed between 0 and 1, and:\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\int_0^1 x \\: dx = \\frac{1}{2} \\; , \\qquad \\int_0^1 \\left(x - \\frac{1}{2}\\right)^2 \\: dx = \\frac{1}{12} \\; .\n",
    "$$\n"
